Encapsulation
- In a single class, bundling data ( fields or variables) and methods that use these data
- controlled access provided

example )
public class Person {
    private String name;
    private int age;

    public String getName(){
        return name;
    }

    public void setName(String name){
        this.name = name;
    }

    public int getAge(){
        return age;
    }

    public void setAge(int age){
    //data validation
        if (age >= 0 && <= 120){
            this.age = age;
        } else
            System.out.println("You entered invalid human age");
    }
}


